nsures that dialogue and lyrics won&#39;t be drowned out by background noise or sound effects. It has a compact design and is lighter than many of the other center channel speakers we reviewed. It is for these reasons that we found the CSi A4 to be the Top Ten Reviews Bronze Award winner."]},"id":"3518f1d9-2665-4b6b-bc01-e5bdc34ff604","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Performance"},"id":"821e618d-d1c7-4762-972e-b49f66bedf56","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The Polk Audio CSi A4 has an overall frequency response of 55Hz to 27kHz. The human hear can audibly hear 20Hz to 20kHz, so this can play the higher frequencies just fine, but it can&#39;t hit the low notes. However, low tones are not as important in center speakers because the subwoofer will handle the lower frequencies."]},"id":"2983f3e9-f4aa-4f45-aaf2-f435c0e4b3f2","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Design"},"id":"583c5df9-94d2-4e3b-b0f2-9be16f19bf46","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Since this Polk Audio product has a nominal impedance of 8 ohms, you&#39;ll want to make sure that your receiver is also rated at 8 ohms or lower. If an audio device is mismatched with a receiver that has a higher rating it will be overloaded and will overheat, causing permanent damage. You can connect the receiver to the unit using 5-way binding posts on the back of the CSi A4.","Efficiency correlates to the sensitivity rating of a product. This center channel speaker has an efficiency rating of 89dB. While this is good, it is among the lowest efficiency ratings in our review. This means that more power will be required to produce sound. It also means that you may hear some hissing or static if this model is turned up to high volume levels."]},"id":"f1a341a1-9d2c-4b7d-ab26-a73f7c4eacc6","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Dimensions"},"id":"285bf087-1672-4262-8cef-3f00ebc4550f","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["This 2-way center speaker has one 1-inch tweeter to handle the high frequency signals. This silk polymer dome tweeter creates a fluid and organic sound as it vibrates back and forth. The CSi A4 also has two 5.25-inch midrange drivers. These drivers feature durable polymer composite construction with rubber surround. Each one of drivers also features Dynamic Balance, which is a process during manufacturing where lasers are used to fine tune audio components."]},"id":"88d01891-998f-47ce-bc7c-b7f393f7da8d","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Help &amp; Support"},"id":"203ba9bd-8544-4fb3-acd5-a22e13371c7f","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["This center speaker is covered by a 5-year warranty. If you have any questions or problems you can contact the Polk Audio customer support team by email or by phone. You can also talk online with a live customer support agent by clicking on the chat icon on their website during business hours. And you can also download the CSi A4 instruction manual from their site."]},"id":"7f2dde69-861a-4115-bfaa-59334a055fda","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"774acbaf-28f1-4895-b38d-6b9441c245fa","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["If you are in need of a new center speaker for your home theater system, the Polk Audio CSi A4 center speaker is a well-constructed piece of audio equipment with high-quality components. It is capable of reproducing high-fidelity sound from a compact design. It may not have the frequency range or sensitivity of other products in our review, but it is still one of the best home theater audio options available."]},"id":"3a078634-edf5-4648-8eba-44fb6e7348b3","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_50509","url":"/polk-audio-csi-a4-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"jonathan-knoder","url":"/author/jonathan-knoder","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Jonathan Knoder","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"yRHneGGUztMrGu99zxra6M","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2010-08-25T22:46:42Z","datePublished":"